description:
One Hundred Great Guns: An Illustrated History of Firearms
Walker & Company | 1967 | ISBN: 0802702058 | English | 386 pages | PDF | 47.4 MB

A detailed history of 100 great guns by the well known gun historian Merrill Lindsay. Illustrated with color and b/w reproductions of photographs and drawings. Photos by Bruce Pendleton and lock illustrations by Peter Parnall
